{"tid":1113760,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞如何不奪歐冠!?","createTime":"2019-04-18T06:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T06:35:28.000Z","uid":227702,"like":13,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"77adf4a1b4b7237e15f3420948fa7331746c2893","tid":1113760,"uid":227702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:03:33.000Z","msg":"作為一個小花迷 咁既四強真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈巴塞拎歐冠有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班小花迷 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先熱刺,唔好玩啦 英超隊，嬴硬<br />\n<br />\n利物浦,,如果係利雲特就有可觀性(順便可以報上次西班牙盃ga仇)(不過算啦,去到西甲又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..出古天奴都夠WIN<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 小花,SO9,馬干,丹比利 加上關鍵王維達爾.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n拎冠就一定..係睇下小花破唔破到歐聯入球記錄.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家奪冠party見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手巴塞..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"6dcf28605fe278ff80948e59dc866e3ae948a581","tid":1113760,"uid":155197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"0e51164504bda3d1b7e70000c2c27d2adacca424","tid":1113760,"uid":245528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eef7bb4a4c48bbb06893b8a3f8ab9e86b7b621d","tid":1113760,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"利物浦,,如果係利雲特就有可觀性(順便可以報上次西班牙盃ga仇)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caab54dd713215e69de67749ee2177bd39432f6a","tid":1113760,"uid":19732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"Is lor you so wise <br />\n不能 agger more"},{"pid":"42b6e356da258608e7bec9014b4af1a70bceacbc","tid":1113760,"uid":156990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"樓豬好撚肉酸好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666729ca1b45c3831b113e5e0e9